    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1941-04-09T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1941-04-09T00:00:00-05:00" n="826"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d826">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">861.5151/190</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Memorandum of Conversation, by the Under Secretary of
                        State</hi> (<hi rend="italic">Welles</hi>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1941-04-09">April 9,
                            1941</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The Soviet Ambassador called to see me this afternoon at his request.</p>
                <p>I told the Ambassador that I had received information concerning the newly
                    imposed exchange rate for rubles in so far as the foreign diplomatic corps in
                    Moscow was concerned and I wished to make it clear that I had no protest to make
                    since there was no element of discrimination involved. Nevertheless, the
                    Ambassador would understand that this implied a very great increase in the cost
                    of our representation in Russia. I suggested to the Ambassador that he request
                    the Counsellor of his Embassy<note n="69" xml:id="d826fn69">Andrey Andreyevich
                        Gromyko. No record of any subsequent talk on this subject has been found in
                        Department files.</note> to talk with Mr. Henderson about this matter so
                    that we might understand the full implications.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>S[<hi rend="smallcaps">umner</hi>] W[<hi rend="smallcaps"
                        >elles</hi>]</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
